 "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "cartservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["currencyservice-2", "recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "frontend-2", "checkoutservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "redis-cart-0"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-20T12:10:27Z to 2025-06-20T12:30:27Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-20 12:10:27+00:00 to 2025-06-20 12:30:27+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["emailservice-1", "frontend-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "frontend-0", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-1", "cartservice-1", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "cartservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["currencyservice-2", "recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "frontend-2", "checkoutservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "redis-cart-0"]}, "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in error_ratio and server_error_ratio during the fault period\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-1 and frontend-2 displayed error_ratio changes from 0% to over 30% with a median change ratio of 2.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Highly increased response time (rrt_max and rrt) indicating potential service bottleneck\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice instances showed rrt_max with a median change from 10-12k to over 5 million, and rrt from under 2k to over 2 million\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Massive spike in rrt_max indicating a potential issue with Redis performance\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis cart had an rrt_max change from 4671 to 845226, indicating severe latency issues\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "### 分析摘要：\n基于提供的调用链数据分析和系统拓扑结构，识别出了显著的异常调用，并对其进行了以下分类和分析。\n\n### 异常特征列表\n从以下调用链数据中发现了几个延迟和错误相关的异常：\n1. **显著延迟**：\n   - `cartservice -> redis` 调用链中，`HGET` 操作的响应时间增长了 **~3400 倍**。\n   - `frontend -> cartservice` 的部分 `POST` 请求响应时间增长了 **~2500倍**。\n   - `checkoutservice -> cartservice` 操作首次引发 `POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart` 的响应时间异常。\n   \n2. **错误状态**：\n   - 多次出现 `HTTP 500` 错误，其中：\n     - `frontend-2` (出现 2360 次)\n     - `frontend-1` (出现 1162 次)\n\n### JSON 格式返回\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"error_500\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis 数据库的 HGET 请求延迟巨大 (3400 倍延迟增长)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"当前正常耗时：~1.7ms，异常耗时：~5900ms，调用链：cartservice-redis\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"与 cartservice 的 POST 请求严重延迟 (2500 倍延迟增长)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常耗时：~2.3ms；异常耗时：~5954+ms，疑似为 redis 问题传播影响\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"checkoutservice 调用 cartservice 的 GetCart 数据接口，高延迟直接传播回入口服务\",\n      \"evidence\": \"操作 POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart 异常耗时为：8000ms\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "log_analysis_findings": "The provided logs reveal a series of errors primarily involving services `frontend` and `cartservice`. The recurring error patterns, particularly `RedisTimeoutException` and connection issues to Redis, suggest failures in accessing or interacting with the Redis backend, which is crucial for cart operations.\n\n### Detected log keys:\n- `RedisTimeoutException`\n- `Can't access cart storage`\n- `Timeout awaiting response`\n- `FailedPrecondition`\n- `connection failed`\n\n### Hypotheses based on prominent fault logs:\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"RedisTimeoutException\",\n    \"Can't access cart storage\",\n    \"Timeout awaiting response\",\n    \"FailedPrecondition\",\n    \"connection failed\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis timeout and connection failures as indicated by `RedisTimeoutException` and `Can't access cart storage`\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Messages such as `Timeout awaiting response ... command=HGET` and `Can't access cart storage` repeated across logs.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Dependent failures due to cartservice issues causing checkout and cart item errors\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Evidence includes log messages like `failed to complete the order` and `failed to add to cart` originating from cartservice interactions.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis instance (redis-cart:6379)\",\n      \"reason\": \"Possible root cause of timeout and connection failures, unclear whether Redis was experiencing overload or configuration issues\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Logs repeated reference the endpoint `redis-cart:6379` with timeout errors, suggesting potential Redis misconfiguration or resource exhaustion.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nBased on the fault logs:\n- The main source of operational anomalies lies within `cartservice`, manifesting in complications accessing Redis storage primarily due to timeout issues (`RedisTimeoutException`).\n- `frontend` service also fails due to its reliance on `cartservice`.\n\nFurther investigation into `redis-cart:6379` is warranted—specifically concerning operational health, connection pool status, and queries causing the timeout/errors."}
